summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Fourteenth Avenue N.E. from Brintnall Place to East Fiftieth Street et al in the City of Seattle, by paving with asphalt under Ordinance No. 18677, creating Local Improvement District No. 1778 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
